          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="3lSwSHziyGCpqqchykvv-15" parent="1" style="shape=umlFrame;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;pointerEvents=0;recursiveResize=0;container=1;collapsible=0;width=160;" value="Agent memory architecture" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="1016" width="1231" x="-2" y="-228" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="3lSwSHziyGCpqqchykvv-16" parent="3lSwSHziyGCpqqchykvv-15" style="shape=note2;boundedLbl=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;size=15;verticalAlign=top;align=left;" value="Architectural and Technical Decisions:&lt;div&gt;1. Apply two type of memory:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- a. Short-term memory: memory type conversation memory to summerize when context too long, Thread-scoped, use langgraph checkpoint checkpoint.&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- b. Long-term memory: Vector Strore Memory,&amp;nbsp;Semantic search over past conversations.&lt;br&gt;2. Checkpointer strategy:&amp;nbsp;LangGraph&#39;s built-in MongoDBSaver checkpointer with pros like native integration and auto-serialization. Therefore, introduce NEW collection dedicated for this purpose.&lt;br&gt;3. Thread ID mapping: using session_id map to LangGraph&#39;s thread_id&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- introduce new collection called &quot;conversation&quot; and map 1-1 to session..&lt;br&gt;4. Memory scopes and limits:&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Support full history (keep all messages), this simplest way but could cause hit limits in long conversation. This need to have memory summary mechanism during long conversation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="210" width="619" x="15" y="37" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="3lSwSHziyGCpqqchykvv-25" parent="3lSwSHziyGCpqqchykvv-15" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="MongoDB&lt;br&gt;agent&lt;div&gt;memory_&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;store&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="73" x="849" y="818" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
